            <div class="architects-header">
                <i class="fas fa-arrow-up architects-icon"></i>
                <h2>Architects Of Our <span class="highlight-text">Organization</span></h2>
                <p>Our organizational architecture is built on a foundation of collaboration and agility. We believe in empowering every team member, fostering an environment where innovation can flourish at every level. This decentralized approach allows us to respond quickly to market changes and customer needs, ensuring we always stay ahead.</p>
            </div>
